I’d rather have Jesus than world-wide fame;
I’d rather be found calling on His name . . .{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}He’s fairer than lilies of rarest bloom;
He’s sweeter than honey from out of the comb
He’s all I could want and He’s all I need;
I’d rather have Jesus and let Him lead.{/lang-eng}
